Package: miu-client
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, python3-pygame, python3-pil, python3-tk
Recommends: python3-pystray
Description: Lightweight Linux client for MIU music streaming
 MIU Client is a minimal audio streaming client that connects to MIU music bot
 servers. It provides:
 .
  * Live audio streaming with embedded metadata
  * Client-side play/pause controls
  * Volume control
  * System tray integration
  * Minimal resource usage
 .
 The client works without authentication and is perfect for listening to
 music streams from MIU Discord bots.